SummaryEnglish: Takuya, Kouji, Izumi, Junpei. and Tomoki meet each other on a train that takes them to the Digital World where a war against evil is being fought. The Angel digimon, Cherubimon, one of the three angels sent to save the world from the power-hungry Lucemon, has turned to the dark side and the entire Digital World is in peril. To fight this great battle, the five CHOSEN ONES must find the Densetsu no Spirit (Legendary Spirit).
TitleJapanese: デジモンフロンティア

1.TitleEnglish: Digimon Frontier: Regeneration of Ancient Digimon
1.SummaryEnglish: The five digi-destined children stumble upon an ancient island inhabited by two different types of digimon; The Beast types, and the Human types. When they see two young digimon-a beast and humanoid-have become friends, they decide something must be done about the feud.
1.TitleJapanese: デジモンフロンティア 古代デジモン復活!!

1.SummaryEnglish: Kids across the city get strange messages on their electronic devices. These messages ask them if they're ready for their future. What do these messages mean?
1.TitleJapanese: 伝説の闘士！炎のアグニモン

2.SummaryEnglish: With one spirit down, the others prepare for their destiny's, but how does one spirit evolve? Does this mean all the kids will become legendary warriors? And how does spirit evolution work?
2.TitleJapanese: 光のヴォルフモン 地下迷宮の戦い！

3.SummaryEnglish: Tomoki wants to learn to spirit evolve, but to get a spirit, he must get through a Candmon village. Can Agnimon help save the day?
3.TitleJapanese: いじめは許さない！氷のチャックモン進化

4.SummaryEnglish: Zoe, JP, Tommy, and Takuya reach a spliting point on the Trailmon tracks. When Takuya and Tommy go one way, it's up to JP and Zoe to save a bunch of Floramon. Can they do so when neither of them has a spirit?
4.TitleJapanese: 私のキックは痛いわよ！女闘士フェアリモン

5.SummaryEnglish: The new digidestined must help a village of Digimon to get free from the Goblimon and Snimon, but can they do so when JP doesn't have a spirit?
5.TitleJapanese: 大地を揺るがす雷パワー ブリッツモン！

6.TitleEnglish: A Molehill Out of a Mountain
6.SummaryEnglish: The KarautsukiNumemon look for help for their village because legendary warriors have taken their womon and childmon hostage, but when they find out the gang is legendary warriors trouble is the result. What exactly is a Beast Spirit, and why is their now a slide evolution? The answers can be found.
6.TitleJapanese: 伝説の５闘士VS新たなる闘士！

7.SummaryEnglish: Takuya's and Koji's differences cause a lot of arguements, but when Tommy gets captured, can they put aside their differences and save him?
7.TitleJapanese: 空に浮かぶ街！トイアグモンのおもちゃの国

8.SummaryEnglish: JP and Zoe arrive at a digimon school where one digimon, Tsunomon, is constantly being ignored. Can the two of them convience the other kids that digivolution isn't a bad thing?
8.TitleJapanese: みんなを救え！進化するんだツノモン

9.SummaryEnglish: Tommy is tricked by a Bakumon causing his dreams to all be evil and make his friends appear evil. Can the digi-destined find a way to save him?
9.TitleJapanese: 敵はチャックモン!?謎のテレビの森

10.SummaryEnglish: The digi-destined figure out that you need a Beast Spirit to defeat a Beast Spirit, but can they find there Beast Spirits before Grumblemon steals all of their spirits?
10.TitleJapanese: ビーストスピリットは制御不能!?ガルムモン進化！

11.SummaryEnglish: When Grottemon isolates koji, the others must find a way to defeat his Beast Spirit. Can Shamamon help them out when he's possessed?
11.TitleJapanese: 俺を倒せ！伝説の闘士ヴリトラモン暴走

12.TitleEnglish: Fear and Loathing in Los Arboles
12.SummaryEnglish: Takuya gains control over his beast spirit, but can he maintain that control when he's forced into a one-on-one battle with Grumblemon?
12.TitleJapanese: ほえろヴリトラモン！倒せギガスモン！

13.TitleEnglish: Better An Egg Than An Egg Shell
13.SummaryEnglish: 4 of the 5 Dark Warriors decide to attack the digi-destined on a quest to gain their spirits. Can a little help from Sorcermon and Seraphimon help them to free the digital world?
13.TitleJapanese: 目覚めよセラフィモン！十闘士の秘密！

14.SummaryEnglish: Grumblemon returns to regain his beast spirit and seperates Takuya and Koji from the rest of the group, but when JP gains his beast spirit can he master it enough to finish off Grumblemon for good?
14.TitleJapanese: 雷よ！岩をも砕け！ボルグモン決死のチャレンジ

15.SummaryEnglish: When the gang decodes to go on a water vacation, the Toucanmon steal the boys D-tectors. Can Zoe save the day without her beast spirit?
15.TitleJapanese: イカしたビースト進化！カルマーラモン

16.SummaryEnglish: A group of Gomamon want to gain access to their island, but it's surronded by whirlpools and Zephrymon guards the way. Can the digi-destined find a way to save the world when the boys still don't have their D-tectors?
16.TitleJapanese: 強いだけじゃダメなのよ！美しき闘士シューツモン

17.SummaryEnglish: Tommy finds the boys D-Tectors at the county fair, but he doesn't have anything to trade to get them back. Can he find something to trade to get them back before the Dark Legendary Warriors show up?
17.TitleJapanese: ブリザーモン 吹けよ雪、呼べよ氷河！

18.SummaryEnglish: The digi-destined stop their battles briefly to participate in the Trailmon races, but can they find a way to stop the normal cheating that occurs?
18.TitleJapanese: チキチキ！トレイルモン猛レース

19.SummaryEnglish: The kids need some food, so they head to the Burgermon village. What will happen when they run into the master of wood?
19.TitleJapanese: バーガモンを救え！友樹のピュアな心

20.SummaryEnglish: Arbormon wants revenge for his missing burgers, so he follows the kids into The Continent of Darkness, but what else has followed there?
20.TitleJapanese: 闇にひそむ謎の闘士 ダスクモン！

21.SummaryEnglish: When Duskmon proves to be too strong for the digi-destined, they have a new decision to make. What will it be?
21.TitleJapanese: 五闘士全滅!?恐るべき闇のパワー！

22.SummaryEnglish: Takuya decides to head home on a Dark Trailmon, but when he gets stuck as a Digimon in the real world, what will he do?
22.TitleJapanese: 我が家へ！拓也たった一人の帰還

23.SummaryEnglish: Takuya returns to the digital world as a stronger Agunimon, but can he save his friends in a classic 2-on-1 showdown?
23.TitleJapanese: 感じろデジモンの力！拓也渾身の作戦

24.SummaryEnglish: When the kids get sucked inside Sakkakumon, they must defeat their opponents and their own self doubts to get free, but will they succeed?
24.TitleJapanese: 対決ボルケーモン！純平、過去との激闘

25.SummaryEnglish: Tommy gets a group of digimon in his dimension who pretend to be his friend, but can he figure out the truth before they steal his D-Tector?
25.TitleJapanese: 友樹の孤独な戦い アシュラモンの罠

26.SummaryEnglish: The fight between Ranamon and Zoe reaches its exciting finale, but who will come out the victor?
26.TitleJapanese: ラーナモンの執念！女デジモン一騎撃ち

27.SummaryEnglish: Koji must battle Duskmon one on one, but will he be able to succeed when they couldn't defeat Duskmon as a team?
27.TitleJapanese: 奇跡のダブルスピリット！ベオウルフモン誕生

28.SummaryEnglish: To get out of Sakkakumon, Takuya must find a way to defeat Mercurymon. Can he find a way to achieve Fusion Evolution and succeed, or are the digi-destined done for in this battle?
28.TitleJapanese: 拓也の融合進化 アルダモン技炸裂！

29.SummaryEnglish: Sakkakumon reveals he is still alive, and now he has the digi-destined's attacks. Can they find a way to create new attacks and defeat Sakkakumon once and for all?
29.TitleJapanese: 逃走！変幻自在セフィロトモン

30.SummaryEnglish: Koji and Kouichi begin to figure out they're related some how, but what is that relation, and can it stop the two of them from destroying each other?
30.TitleJapanese: 飛翔！闇の闘士ベルグモン

31.SummaryEnglish: JP, Zoe, and Tommy decide to discover what horrors await them at the Rose Morning Star by searching a Trailmon graveyard, but what horrors await them inside the graveyard?
31.TitleJapanese: 闇に眠る トレイルモンの墓場

32.SummaryEnglish: When Koji realizes he has a brother and has been fighting him, he refuses to fight anymore. Can Takuya make him see the truth?
32.TitleJapanese: 明かされた過去！ダスクモンの秘密

33.SummaryEnglish: Now that he's a regular human again, Kouichi decides to join the digi-destined, but can he find a way to help them out without any spirits of his own to use?
33.TitleJapanese: 新たなる闇の闘士！レーベモン＆カイザーレオモン

34.SummaryEnglish: The digidestined decide to free Ophanimon once and for all, but Cherubimon ends up being her guard. Can they find a way to free her from the final of the 3 guardian Digimon?
34.TitleJapanese: 決戦！バラの明星 オファニモン救出作戦

35.SummaryEnglish: Takuya and Koji must hold off Cherubimon while the others free Ophanimon, but can they succeed when they lose their spirits?
35.TitleJapanese: スピリットを一つに！拓也と輝二の究極進化

36.SummaryEnglish: Cherubimon appears to be defeated, but he appears to be easy compared to IceDevimon. Can the others find a way to defeat IceDevimon with Takuya and Koji's D-Tectors frozen solid?
36.TitleJapanese: 勝利への飛翔！対決ケルビモンの城

37.SummaryEnglish: The final battle between EmperorGreymon/ MagnaGarurumon and Cherubimon begins, but who will end up being the victor, and who are these mysterious characters that are watching the battle?
37.TitleJapanese: 決戦！命ある限り デジタルワールドを取り戻せ

38.SummaryEnglish: The Royal Knights appears and reveal that Lucemon will return. Can the digi-destined find a way to prevent this chaos from occuring,or will they be delaying the inevitable?
38.TitleJapanese: 終わらない死闘！ルーチェモン復活の序曲

39.TitleEnglish: The Man in the Moon Is You
39.SummaryEnglish: After waking up on the moon, the digi-destined decide to try to get back to the digital world to get revenge on the Royal Knights, but will they succeed, or will they be stuck on the moon for the rest of their lives?
39.TitleJapanese: これがデジタルワールド!?月からの脱出！

40.SummaryEnglish: The digidestined run into the same group of kids that pushed Tommy onto the train causing him to come into the digital world, but can Tommy get past his resentment of them and save the day?
40.TitleJapanese: 選ばれし者!?エンジェモンを操る少年！

41.SummaryEnglish: Katshuhara and company have been captured by the Royal Knights. It's a good thing for them that Tommy is with them, but can they find a way to save Beanstalk Village, and can the other kids get Worm the Trailmon to want to help out?
41.TitleJapanese: スキャンさせるな！友情の豆の木

42.SummaryEnglish: When the Royal Knights target the Village og Beginnings for their next assault, it's up to the kids to convience the Trailmon to save the digi-eggs, but can they finally defeat the Royal Knights? Maybe they can with help from some old enemies.
42.TitleJapanese: デジタマを守れ！消えゆく命の奇跡

43.SummaryEnglish: The kids rush to try and save the Flame Terminal from being deleted, but with the SkullSatamon already on hand, can they find a way to defeat them? Is there any way to unite all the Digimon to fight together?
43.TitleJapanese: 故郷消滅！地獄の使者スカルサタモン

44.TitleEnglish: Now You See It, Now You Don't
44.SummaryEnglish: With only 3 areas left to protect in the digital world, the digi-destined must act fast to save the forest terminal. EmperorGreymon and MagnaGarurumon seem to be getting stronger, but will they finally be able to defeat the Royal Knights?
44.TitleJapanese: 共に戦え！ゴツモンと輝二の誓い

45.TitleEnglish: All Aboard The Tag Team Express
45.SummaryEnglish: Only 2 areas of the digital world remain: The Autumn Leaf Fair and Ophanimon's castle, but can the kids find a way to save The Fair without losing any more digimon friends, or is the digital world truly done for?
45.TitleJapanese: データかく乱作戦！アキバマーケットを防衛せよ

46.TitleEnglish: To Make The World Go Away
46.SummaryEnglish: The digi-destined arrive at Ophanimon's castle to try and save the last bit of data from being given to Lucemon. Can they finally defeat the Royal Knights, or will Lucemon be reborn?
46.TitleJapanese: デジタルワールド消滅!?ルーチェモン暗黒支配

47.SummaryEnglish: The final battle with the Royal Knights is about to occur, but who will win this surprising bout?
47.TitleJapanese: ロイヤルナイツ散る そして…!!

48.SummaryEnglish: Since Emperor Greymon and MagnaGarurumon proved to be too weak, the kids decide to try a multi attack, but will it be enough, or will they need additional power?
48.TitleJapanese: 光と闇を一つに！輝一最後の願い

49.SummaryEnglish: Susannomon has been born, but will the combined powers of all 10 legendary spirits be enough to defeat Lucemon for good, or does Lucemon have one final surprise in store?
49.TitleJapanese: 戦えスサノオモン ルーチェモン人間界到達!!

50.SummaryEnglish: The final battle between Lucemon and Susanoomon will be decided not in the digital world, but in the real world. Who will end up prevailing in this free for all?
50.TitleJapanese: 時を越えて！新たな伝説の始まり
